Package: xft2
Version: 2.1.3
Revision: 1
BuildDepends: fontconfig2, freetype2 | freetype2-hinting, render1-dev, x11-dev, xrender1
Depends: %N-shlibs
Source: http://freedesktop.org/~xlibs/release/libXft-%v.tar.bz2
Source-MD5: 6b6880fb1102ce21de39fd03630578da
ConfigureParams: --prefix=%p/lib/%N --sysconfdir=/private/etc --bindir=%p/bin --mandir=%p/share/man
CompileScript: <<
#!/bin/sh

  export PKG_CONFIG_PATH=%p/lib/render1/lib/pkgconfig:%p/lib/fontconfig2/lib/pkgconfig:%p/lib/xrender1/lib/pkgconfig
  ./configure %c
  make
<<
InstallScript: <<
 make -j1 install DESTDIR=%d
<<
SplitOff: <<
  Package: %N-shlibs
  Depends: fontconfig2-shlibs, freetype2-shlibs | freetype2-hinting-shlibs, x11, xrender1-shlibs
  Files: lib/%N/lib/libXft.*.dylib
  Shlibs: %p/lib/%N/lib/libXft.2.dylib 4.0.0 (%n >= 2.1.3-1)
  Description: Shared libraries for libXft
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog INSTALL NEWS README
License: OSI-Approved
Description: Libraries and development headers for the X freetype extension
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <ranger@befunk.com>
Homepage: http://freedesktop.org/~xlibs/
DescPackaging: <<
This package should not be linked against unless absolutely
necessary.  If you must link against it, you may need to set
some variables.

  CPPFLAGS:        add -I%p/lib/%N/include
  CFLAGS:          you might need the same as CPPFLAGS
  PKG_CONFIG_PATH: add %p/lib/%N/lib/pkgconfig
<<
